(n, k) = map(int, input().split())
tweets = [False] * n
num_open = 0
for i in range(k):
    cmd = input().split()
    if cmd[0] == 'CLICK':
        tweet_id = int(cmd[1]) - 1
        if tweets[tweet_id]:
            tweets[tweet_id] = False
            num_open -= 1
        else:
            tweets[tweet_id] = True
            num_open += 1
    else:
        tweets = [False] * n
        num_open = 0
    print(num_open)

(n, k) = map(int, input().split())
status = [0] * n
status_total = 0
for _ in range(k):
    s = input()
    if s == 'CLOSEALL':
        status = [0] * n
        status_total = 0
    else:
        s = s.split()
        s = int(s[1]) - 1
        if status[s]:
            status_total -= 1
        else:
            status_total += 1
        status[s] = 1 - status[s]
    print(status_total)
